284
00:10:25,250 --> 00:10:26,783
I don't know what kind of law
you're teaching around here,

285
00:10:26,835 --> 00:10:28,668
but where I come from,
you show up on time.

286
00:10:28,703 --> 00:10:31,121
Let's go.

287
00:10:31,173 --> 00:10:32,105
