that might get her sued.

304
00:11:07,175 --> 00:11:09,008
Dr. Gwendolyn Barnes?

305
00:11:09,044 --> 00:11:10,477
Do you have
a problem with her?

306
00:11:10,512 --> 00:11:12,278
No, not at all.
