out of your head.

340
00:12:42,611 --> 00:12:45,195
People tell you
it's part of God's plan.

341
00:12:45,231 --> 00:12:48,198
Maybe they're right,
but it doesn't stop you

342
00:12:48,234 --> 00:12:49,566
from wanting
to punch them in the face

343
