as long as it did,

359
00:13:44,690 --> 00:13:48,492
it took a while
to work out the particulars.

360
00:13:48,527 --> 00:13:51,695
But I can assure you,

361
00:13:51,730 --> 00:13:53,230
it's worth the wait,

362
00:13:53,265 --> 00:13:55,565
because this right here,

363
00:13:55,601 --> 00:14:00,137
