partner."

371
00:14:19,141 --> 00:14:20,273
What the hell
are you talking about?

372
00:14:20,326 --> 00:14:21,692
You're the one
that said it yourself.

373
00:14:21,744 --> 00:14:23,493
You and me,
we're the all-star team.

374
00:14:23,529 --> 00:14:25,829
